# Firebase google-services.json
# A placeholder google-services.json IS committed so dev builds + EAS bundling
# resolve the app.json `googleServicesFile` reference without erroring. Before
# the Android production build, replace mobile/google-services.json with the
# real file from console.firebase.google.com → Project Settings → Android app
# (package: me.burs.app). The real file may contain project-scoped API keys
# and should NOT be committed — when swapping in the real file locally, untrack
# it first (`git rm --cached mobile/google-services.json`) so subsequent commits
# don't accidentally publish production credentials. FCM push silently fails
# until the real file ships.
